item.description:
We had so much fun last year, we are going to try it again! Please join me at the second annual Wings and Wheels event. It will be held a little eariler this year, so it shuold be a little warmer. Please come and help and/or just to enjoy the show. There will be tons of classic cars, locally based airplanes, airplanes flying in, new airplane vendors, and more.

Please come bring out your airplane, help run the show, and look at the neat cars and planes.

Show runs 10:00am to 3:00pm. Come at 7:00am to help setup if able.
